-<a href="http://HavenWorks.com/politics"><img SRC="images/navigation/indexbox/HavenGIFs/thumbs/POLITICS-NEWS-POLITICAL-NEWS-HavenWorks-com.GIF" ALT="POLITICIAN News. POLITICS News." NOSAVE TITLE="POLITICIAN News. POLITICS News." height=14 width=26></a><b><a href="http://HavenWorks.com/politics">Politics</a></b>
