<br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, verdana, Variable Width"><font size=-1>"</font><b><a href="http://tpmmuckraker.talkingpointsmemo.com/2009/02/source_collins_strips_stim_bill_of_whistleblower_p.php">Source:
