<center><font face="Arial, Helvetica, verdana, Variable Width"><font size=-1>"</font><b><a href="http://www.dispatchpolitics.com/live/content/local_news/stories/2009/02/10/copy/caproos.html?adsec=politics&sid=101">U.S.
