-&nbsp;<a href="http://HavenWorks.com/accounting"><img SRC="images/navigation/indexbox/HavenGIFs/thumbs/ACCOUNTING-News-HavenWorks-.gif" ALT="ACCOUNTING News." NOSAVE TITLE="ACCOUNTING News. AUDIT News." height=14 width=26></a><b><font size=+1><a href="http://HavenWorks.com/accounting">Accounting</a></font></b>
